## `test_reopen_preserves_xattrs(tmp_db)`
<!-- checksum: placeholder-dura-6 -->

### Postconditions

```python
mkfs(str(tmp_db))

fs = open_fs(str(tmp_db))
with fs.as_user(0, 0):
    fd = fs.create("/f"); fs.close_fd(fd)
    fs.setxattr("/f", "user.a", b"1")
    fs.setxattr("/f", "user.b", b"two")
fs.close()

fs = open_fs(str(tmp_db))
with fs.as_user(0, 0):
    assert sorted(fs.listxattr("/f")) == ["user.a", "user.b"]
    assert fs.getxattr("/f", "user.a") == b"1"
    assert fs.getxattr("/f", "user.b") == b"two"
fs.close()
```

