## `test_reopen_preserves_symlinks(tmp_db)`
<!-- checksum: placeholder-dura-7 -->

### Postconditions

```python
mkfs(str(tmp_db))

fs = open_fs(str(tmp_db))
with fs.as_user(0, 0):
    fs.symlink(b"\x80\x81/non-utf8/target", "/link")
fs.close()

